of old times?

881
00:38:27,580 --> 00:38:28,980
They're different.

882
00:38:29,220 --> 00:38:30,780
Sour chicken? Cloudy soup?
[*"Levirate marriage" was misheard.]

883
00:38:37,500 --> 00:38:38,700
The chicken isn't sour!

884
00:38:39,020 --> 00:38:40,660
And the soup isn't cloudy either!

885
00:38:46,140 --> 00:38:48,260
