886
00:38:51,220 --> 00:38:52,540
I need to think.

887
00:38:52,580 --> 00:38:55,300
Come on. We're running out of time.

888
00:38:55,500 --> 00:38:56,820
You heard Song said

889
00:38:56,940 --> 00:38:58,180
the apothecary didn't open today.

890
00:38:58,180 --> 00:38:59,180
The clerks were taking stock.

891
00:38:59,180 --> 00:39:00,300
So, what does this mean?

892
00:39:01,540 --> 00:39:04,580
It means
Shaohua is about to entrust it.

893
00:39:13,580 --> 00:39:14,140
I…

894
00:39:38,420 --> 00:39:39,540
Grandma.

895
00:39:41,140 --> 00:39:42,900
My sweetheart.

896
00:39:44,100 --> 00:39:45,460
Do you miss me?

897
00:39:48,180 --> 00:39:49,660
Mother, please have a seat.

898
00:39:51,300 --> 00:39:53,100
Are you busy?

899
00:39:55,780 --> 00:39:57,580
I came by today

900
00:39:57,860 --> 00:40:00,860
to apologize to you.

901
00:40:01,380 --> 00:40:03,620
Yesterday

902
00:40:03,620 --> 00:40:04,580
I got so flustered

903
00:40:04,580 --> 00:40:06,860
and ended up saying harsh words.

904
00:40:07,300 --> 00:40:09,140
Please don't take it to heart.

905
00:40:09,460 --> 00:40:11,380
Don't let these petty matters

906
00:40:11,420 --> 00:40:13,900
ruin our family harmony.

907
00:40:13,940 --> 00:40:14,620
Mother,

908
00:40:15,140 --> 00:40:16,900
what do you want?

909
00:40:18,220 --> 00:40:18,860
I

910
00:40:18,860 --> 00:40:21,460
just want to tell you

911
00:40:21,460 --> 00:40:22,940
how I feel.

912
00:40:23,500 --> 00:40:24,420
It's been so many years.

913
00:40:24,460 --> 00:40:25,180
When you first came

914
00:40:25,460 --> 00:40:27,900
to the Chen family,

915
00:40:28,180 --> 00:40:29,140
back then,

916
00:40:29,140 --> 00:40:31,180
I was indeed critical of you.

917
00:40:32,300 --> 00:40:34,220
But that was
due to the Chen family's traditions.

918
00:40:35,260 --> 00:40:36,580
Over all these years,

919
00:40:36,740 --> 00:40:38,420
so many things have happened.

920
00:40:39,300 --> 00:40:41,220
I know

921
00:40:41,820 --> 00:40:42,900
you're reasonable

922
00:40:44,060 --> 00:40:44,660
and capable.

923
00:40:45,140 --> 00:40:46,500
You're good to me.

924
00:40:46,980 --> 00:40:49,500
Your mother is good to me.

925
00:40:53,060 --> 00:40:54,020
Don't you feel it?

926
00:40:54,020 --> 00:40:56,500
The way I treat you now

927
00:40:56,500 --> 00:40:58,660
has completely changed,

928
00:40:58,940 --> 00:40:59,700
right?

929
00:41:03,860 --> 00:41:06,940
Mother, it all came out

930
00:41:06,940 --> 00:41:08,220
