935
00:41:19,020 --> 00:41:21,180
I just want to ask.

936
00:41:22,420 --> 00:41:24,580
Could you please not leave?
Stay with us.

937
00:41:24,580 --> 00:41:26,140
We can't manage without you.

938
00:41:26,660 --> 00:41:30,180
I can't leave without you or Xuan.

939
00:41:31,060 --> 00:41:33,340
If you agree to stay,

940
00:41:34,860 --> 00:41:35,980
I promise

941
00:41:35,980 --> 00:41:37,260
